data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!  Custom built one owner, all brick home in immaculate condition. Step inside of this spacious home with a sun room, family room, living room, large kitchen with island, pantry, built ins and custom oak cabinets,  primary bedroom with private bath and walk-in closet, plus another bedroom with walk-in closet and solid doors throughout.  The full walk-out basement is huge with finished ceilings - great for future living space.  400 AMP electric service.  And lets not forget the garage/shop downstairs that has heat and air, own back yard concrete driveway.  Main level oversized garage has heat  and air also.  Lots of storage areas.  New metal roof, nice front porch and wonderful yard.
